{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"4c802ee4ab","title":"反对马克思列宁主义的右派言论","origin":"《右派言论集》（河南医学院马列主义教研室编印，1958年4月）。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"afaf8925df","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"4c802ee4ab"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"00d8e3d85b","name":"河南医学院"},{"id":"3498efbe20","name":"李华峰"},{"id":"62223ebeb6","name":"黄德元"},{"id":"a61f8f95b0","name":"宁文俞"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"22217e08e7","type":"title","text":"反对马克思列宁主义的右派言论","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4c802ee4ab"},{"id":"b2f5625d18","type":"authors","text":"河南医学院宁文俞黄德元李华峰","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4c802ee4ab"},{"id":"a8e206b21a","type":"paragraph","text":"马克思主义现在有好些不适用了，不是那么神圣。马克思是100多年前的人，咋能看到今天。(宁文俞，工会文化教员)","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4c802ee4ab"},{"id":"f0a9875b36","type":"paragraph","text":"马克思主义既是放至四海而皆准的真理，为什么有许多人不能接受？例如杜勒斯还说他们是真理。我认为真理是在历史发展阶段中大家公认的就是真理。例如上帝创造人（真理），能解释人的起源就是真理；又如在封建社会里人们都信佛教，所以佛教就是真理。(黄德元，26期学生)","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4c802ee4ab"},{"id":"59f286394d","type":"paragraph","text":"阶级已不存在，用阶级眼光去分析是错误的。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4c802ee4ab"},{"id":"c43f5148cf","type":"paragraph","text":"人是自私的动物，大脑皮层是自私的产物，人不为己、天诛地灭，官大官小挣钱就好。(李华峰，25期学生)","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4c802ee4ab"}],"page":{"id":"e55cc534fa","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4c802ee4ab","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}